{"tid":1373752,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(徹查) 邊啲鬼叫「前線共識730散」?","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T19:58:59.000Z","uid":83477,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fb5d6cddfa0b253dbb2cdf7d435d934b681c3fa2","tid":1373752,"uid":83477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:13:07.000Z","msg":"實有好多負評<br />\n條氣唔順   又被迫走既手足<br />\n希望幫幫手<br />\n咁搞法每次都係誤傳前線既意願<br />\n<br />\n發夢現場<br />\n人分兩邊<br />\n完全無討論<br />\n點解會又出現上環咁 鳩up 前線共識?<br />\n個人認為有鬼鳩傳消息<br />\n破壞運動<br />\n必須徹查<br />\n<br />\n暫時搵到tg 城大xxxxx<br />\n係[1911]出左 前線話7:30走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBr2vkz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBr2vkz.jpg&h=3fc45977&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a0a4bdbc3768bdbaa46d1dd7093adba61553b66","tid":1373752,"uid":87625,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"推返d有意義野 捉鬼無意思<br />\n加油 聽日下場仗"},{"pid":"16c47b6d8eb01643666636bbd725c8f0a02135af","tid":1373752,"uid":4105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:15:42.000Z","msg":"屌晒佢哋老母<br />\n邊個叫撤，邊個係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af88dfe49a989247f9bc4fbef7defa83d7c1d046","tid":1373752,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山 各自努力"},{"pid":"4fd54cb200712ba40fc22cde1059b926e5f6ac37","tid":1373752,"uid":258956,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1a0a4bdbc3768bdbaa46d1dd7093adba61553b66","tid":1373752,"uid":87625,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"推返d有意義野 捉鬼無意思<br />\n加油 聽日下場仗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:16:18.000Z","msg":"捉鬼無意思？屌你呀"},{"pid":"ba52c9ad3444d425c8da6861c27fed44fe75189e","tid":1373752,"uid":274085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"必須查！"},{"pid":"348477e77c1a3cc74ade4f98eb8a4288c95d3940","tid":1373752,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:17:26.000Z","msg":"依個post 19:07已經講緊前線決定1930撤退<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1372091/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1372091/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"cd9be54b929975a599d45fe1f4773421bcfab1ef","tid":1373752,"uid":288140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:20:55.000Z","msg":"自己衡量風險，有危險就走，次次等埋發叔好易送頭，場運動無搞手，好難達共識。前線見人開始少就要散，be water"},{"pid":"f8090b48cf22194a19644abbb411eeaac6ebea93","tid":1373752,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"直播post就19:09:27先有人講1930散<br />\n<br />\n［置頂］元朗現場直播<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/buMECENZ\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/buMECENZ</a>"},{"pid":"59e2cde350e99b7208f236e6b04d07873cdbe4ad","tid":1373752,"uid":83477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:31:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔走仲要屌人唔走</span></span>"},{"pid":"a115a32c42f6895a769789d767be474f15251de7","tid":1373752,"uid":83477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46dd8467fbee9e9f79572ca0045b884a79eb11ff","tid":1373752,"uid":147895,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:36:06.000Z","msg":"前線唔止一條，加上有啲勇武唔阻止其他人退不過自己唔會退，所以可能造成左資訊傳遞錯誤嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有鬼玩假情報，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地而家開始應該諗個方法去確認消息真偽，去破解呢招，而唔係專注係捉隻鬼出黎，今日已經過左，但日後一定會再發現同類型情況。</span><br />\n<br />\n往好處諗，有位俾鬼入啫係我地係呢個位做得唔夠好，每次有鬼搞破壞但瓦解唔到我地，都只會令我地成個系統更加完善。<br />\n<br />\n發夢聽到開始傳730一齊走嘅位置的確係好前傳去後面，而且大部份現場嘅人睇黎都認同所以句野傳得好快。"},{"pid":"d6931776b9a55e67a23223f8eb5f15416a8a0e6b","tid":1373752,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"勇武決定左要留，已經做好比攻擊準備，<br />\n真正留喺現場嘅勇武兄弟，<br />\n係唔會怪自已人離開，<br />\n同時都唔希望有人set死線幾時走，<br />\n即使離開現場，<br />\n和理非心中都會支持留守兄弟決定，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留下：支持；離開：專重</span></span><br />\n有班3毛扮勇武屌自己人散水，<br />\n和理非唔好被影響到<br />\n<br />\n勇武其實已經有左付死嘅決心，<br />\n死都唔怕，點會怕比人拉同比人打，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武在乎嘅係用自己嘅生命去揭露政權嘅邪惡，</span></span><br />\n我地應該給予最大專重同支持，<br />\n留低嘅人就盡量留到最後，<br />\n直至政府宣布特赦呢班義士為止<br />\n<br />\n【散水】有份叫人730走嘅入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1373646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1373646</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"57722cd6ded4ba111b1a0db3a9d0ed80bdc49d24","tid":1373752,"uid":83477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"先唔好假設係群體既錯<br />\n捉唔到來源 點落去"},{"pid":"826b4a815f1bf1132f4c857ad974a84288fca5a6","tid":1373752,"uid":83477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:15:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc241468229e21891284d739885ae2a569e932a9","tid":1373752,"uid":51111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"發夢小綜合同個人見解。( 和理非同勇武都入！！)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374133\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374133</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ae88d8da5651862976d7bfef47a0f5f88c010ac","tid":1373752,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:32:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">防護裝備用完唔好亂掉，呢啲唔係武器，俾人搜到都唔怕。<br />\n如果俾人查身份證都驚就唔好學人講抗爭。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">黑警問點解帶防具出街，你就答：</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>而家警察落閘唔出勤，市民戴保護裝備出街好合理！警察盡責嘅話，我洗攞咁多重野出街食飯？！</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">今晚727有兩個情況嚴重，希望平安無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以話防具好重要</span><br />\n[多圖]純防護裝備：頭盔、盾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372308\"